title: First Day of a New Project
content: Started working on the CipherGUI project. Feeling optimistic about the progress and challenges ahead.

title: Holiday Trip
content: Took a short trip to the mountains. The fresh air was exactly what I needed to clear my head.

title: Presentation Day

title: Refactoring Old Code
content: Decided to refactor the UI manager. It's a lot of work, but it will be worth it for maintainability.
